OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784926088
OL,3,CMore than 100 firefighters at major
OL,4,Cfire in Essex following explosion
OL,6,FMore than 100 firefighters are
OL,7,Ftackling a major fire that has broken
OL,8,Fout at an industrial site in Essex.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,11,Flarge blaze on Southend Road, between
OL,12,FEast Hanningfield and Rettendon, on
OL,13,FFriday afternoon.
OL,15,FResidents described seeing and feeling
OL,16,Fan explosion at the site.
OL,18,FHuge clouds of black smoke could be
OL,19,Fseen spiralling into the air.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
