OL,3,CMore than 100 firefighters at major
OL,4,Cfire in Essex following explosion
OL,6,FThose living in the area have been
OL,7,Ftold by Essex County Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService to keep their windows and
OL,9,Fdoors closed.
OL,11,F"Over 100 firefighters are working to
OL,12,Fextinguish the fire in Southend Road,"
OL,13,Fthe service said in a statement.
OL,15,F"Please continue to avoid the area,
OL,16,Fand keep your windows and doors closed
OL,17,Fif you live nearby."
OL,19,FThis is a breaking news story, more to
OL,20,Ffollow soon...
